</ul>
<p><strong>5. What is the Significance of the Series?</strong></p>
<p>"The Chronicles of Narnia" is a beloved children's fantasy series that has sold over 100 million copies worldwide. It has been translated into dozens of languages and has been adapted into several films, television shows, and video games. The series has had a profound impact on readers of all ages, inspiring creativity, imagination, and a sense of wonder.</p>